Package com.spectralogic.ds3client.helpers.channelbuilders

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IoLoggingChannelBuilder
    This ObjectChannelBuilder is used to wrap an existing ObjectChannelBuilder and wrap all the channels it creates in a logging channel to log how many bytes were read or written on each call.
    ObjectInputStreamBuilder
    Writes a file to an input stream to be used when performing a write job with Ds3ClientHelpers.startWriteJob(String, Iterable) and performing the transfer with Ds3ClientHelpers.Job#transfer(Ds3ClientHelpers.ObjectChannelBuilder)
    ObjectOutputStreamBuilder
    Writes a file to an output stream to be used when performing a read job with Ds3ClientHelpers.startReadJob(String, Iterable) and performing the transfer with Ds3ClientHelpers.Job#transfer(Ds3ClientHelpers.ObjectChannelBuilder)
    PrefixAdderObjectChannelBuilder  
    PrefixRemoverObjectChannelBuilder
    Writes files to the local file system with a different path by first stripping off a remote prefix and then adding a local prefix.
    ReadOnlySeekableByteChannel  
    WriteOnlySeekableByteChannel
